    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically robust 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera (996.2). This example features the 3.6L naturally aspirated flat-six engine, utilizing VarioCam Plus for an optimized torque curve across the rev range. The 6-speed G96 manual transaxle offers crisp gear engagement, paired with a chassis that retains its factory-spec lateral stiffness and damping characteristics. Significantly, the IMS bearing and Rear Main Seal (RMS) have been proactively serviced, mitigating common failure points of the M96 architecture. The vehicle presents with a clean undercarriage and consistent compression across all cylinders. This is a high-functioning driver\u2019s car that balances visceral feedback with German engineering precision.",
